@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place "Building" where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files or
Libraries are needed.

                             How to play?

  To turn a light on or off, just click on a window (windows are the
ones with a white or black filled rectangle), this will toggle it on or
off, depending on its state. In addition, clicking on a window may
toggle on or off a number of other windows.

  If you get tired or just want to restart a new game (with all the
lights turned on) click on the "New Game" button located on top of the
building (or in the '@{b}Game@{ub}' pull-down menu, select '@{b}New Game@{ub}', you
can also use the @{b}Right-Amiga@{ub} and '@{b}N@{ub}' keys).

  Have fun!

@endnode

